  ('elementary-8b44517b-moex-00383', 'elementary-8b44517b', 'elementary-8b44517b-moex-113-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-8b44517b-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲對於警察機關委託之拖吊業者不滿，當拖吊業者在交通頻繁之處所執行拖吊勤務時，對拖吊業者比中指 侮辱之。甲之行為如何評價？', '["無罪", "公然侮辱罪", "侮辱公務員罪", "妨害秩序罪"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4cff5c1bfc40", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f53769d74470", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "503", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 43, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-8b44517b-moex-00384', 'elementary-8b44517b', 'elementary-8b44517b-moex-113-55d283b0', 'sub-elementary-8b44517b-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於加重結果犯之敘述，何者錯誤？', '["刑法第17條之加重結果犯，以能預見加重結果之發生為要件", "刑法第17條之加重結果犯係故意的基本犯罪與過失加重結果之結合犯罪", "不論法有無明文規定，客觀上可能預見加重結果，即足以構成加重結果犯", "就加重結果之發生，具有主觀過失，方能構成"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:31+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4cff5c1bfc40", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f53769d74470", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113010", "c": "503", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "法學大意", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
